				<font face="Verdana" size="1"><b>best</b></font>
			</td>
		</td>
		
	
	</tr>
	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This spell takes longer to cast than your last charm.  Your stun will wear off before you are done casting it.  Unless you can channel thru two rounds of getting hit, don't rely on the stun/charm combo you used to, if you ever did.  Now is the time to master the stun/lvl 4 Mez/charm combo that you might have heard about.  You need it at this point.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
